User stories for the user frontend:

As a user, I should be able to view the menu./
As a user, I should be able to login and logout /
As a user, I should be able to add items to my cart.
As a user, I should be able to checkout and place an order.
<!-- As a user, I should be able to track the status of my order. -->
As a user, I should be able to add items to my favorites list./
<!-- As a user, I should be able to leave reviews for the food and service I have received. -->
As a user, I should be able to contact the restaurant directly if I have any questions or concerns.
As a user, I should be able to receive push notifications about my orders.
<!-- As a user, I should be able to share my orders on social media. -->


User stories for the admin frontend:

As an admin, I should be able to manage the menu.
As an admin, I should be able to login and logout /
As an admin, I should be able to view orders./
As an admin, I should be able to process orders.
As an admin, I should be able to manage users./
As an admin, I should be able to have a dashboard./
<!-- As an admin, I should be able to view reports. -->
As an admin, I should be able to store data.
<!-- As an admin, I should be able to generate reports. -->
As an admin, I should be able to send notifications.